title: Scale AI acquires SiaSearch to give companies the same data engine superpowers that Tesla has
text: Scale AI, the five-year-old visual data labeling company, has acquired a small startup that could help expand its reach in Europe and speed up development of its newest product. Financial terms were not disclosed.

title: Tesla To Make Its EVs Available To Uber's London Drivers: Report
text: Uber Technologies Inc (NYSE: UBER) is looking to expand its green energy drive to the U.K.  What Happened: Ride-hailing company Uber has struck a deal with Tesla Inc (NASDAQ: TSLA) to provide London drivers access to Tesla's EVs, according to media reports.

title: Tesla's latest patch hints at cloud-synced driver profiles
text: Tesla is preparing for a world where your driver profile can follow you across different cars, be it yours or a rental. The car maker added a Cloud Profiles section in its latest software release.

title: Why Tesla Stock Jumped on Wednesday
text: The electric-car maker's stock caught a wave during an upbeat day in the overall market.
